graph TB
    subgraph "ModelMesh Serving Component"
        Controller[modelmesh-controller<br/>Deployment]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>ValidatingWebhook]
        PredictorCtrl[predictor-controller]
        RuntimeCtrl[servingruntime-controller]
        ServiceCtrl[service-controller]

        Controller -->|validates| Webhook
        Controller -->|contains| PredictorCtrl
        Controller -->|contains| RuntimeCtrl
        Controller -->|contains| ServiceCtrl
    end

    subgraph "Per-Namespace Runtime Deployment"
        MMRuntime[modelmesh-runtime<br/>Deployment]
        MMContainer[ModelMesh Container<br/>Java Routing Layer]
        ServerContainer[Model Server<br/>Triton/MLServer/OpenVINO/TorchServe]
        AdapterContainer[Runtime Adapter<br/>Model Puller]

        MMRuntime -->|contains| MMContainer
        MMRuntime -->|contains| ServerContainer
        MMRuntime -->|contains| AdapterContainer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        PredictorCR[Predictor CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntimeCR[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        etcd[etcd<br/>StatefulSet<br/>Distributed State]
        S3[S3/MinIO<br/>Model Storage]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        Istio[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>Optional mTLS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus Operator<br/>Metrics Collection]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Webhook Certs]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    User -->|creates| PredictorCR
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntimeCR

    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| PredictorCtrl
    PredictorCR -->|watched by| PredictorCtrl
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| RuntimeCtrl
    ClusterServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| RuntimeCtrl

    PredictorCtrl -->|creates| MMRuntime
    RuntimeCtrl -->|configures| MMRuntime
    ServiceCtrl -->|creates| MMService[ModelMesh Service<br/>ClusterIP]

    MMContainer -->|routes to| ServerContainer
    AdapterContainer -->|pulls models from| S3
    MMContainer -->|state coordination| etcd

    Controller -->|watches CRDs via| K8sAPI
    Webhook -->|called by| K8sAPI

    MMRuntime -.->|optional mTLS| Istio
    Controller -->|exposes metrics to| Prometheus
    Webhook -.->|TLS cert from| CertManager

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MMRuntime fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PredictorCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ClusterServingRuntimeCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style etcd fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertManager fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
